OL,3,CGirl, 8, in serious condition in
OL,4,Chospital following crash
OL,6,FAn eight-year-old girl is in a serious
OL,7,Fcondition in hospital after a crash in
OL,8,FDumfries and Galloway.
OL,10,FThe incident happened at around
OL,11,F10.50am on Tuesday, 27 May 2025, on
OL,12,Fthe A747 Glenluce to Glasserton road
OL,13,Fnear Monreith.
OL,15,FIt involved a black Mitsubishi L200
OL,16,Fcar and a pedestrian.
