OL,3,CGirl, 8, in serious condition in
OL,4,Chospital following crash
OL,6,FThe pedestrian, an eight-year-old
OL,7,Fgirl, was taken to the Queen Elizabeth
OL,8,FUniversity Hospital in Glasgow for
OL,9,Ftreatment, where she remains in a
OL,10,Fserious condition. There were no other
OL,11,Finjuries.
OL,13,FThe road was closed for around eight
OL,14,Fhours to allow enquiries to be carried
OL,15,Fout.
OL,17,FRoad Policing Sergeant Colin Ramage
OL,18,Fsaid: "Our enquiries remain ongoing to
OL,19,Festablish the full circumstances of
OL,20,Fthis crash and I would appeal to any
OL,21,Fwitnesses to please contact police.
